data.text: i even think andrew lloyd webber HIMSELF said that gerard’s voice is the ideal phantom voice so anyone who wants to come for me can talk to the HAND

i think it’s just how his voice contrasts so deeply with christine’s voice and it’s still moderately good like i KNOW he’s not the best but there’s a definite contrast between the husk of his voice and the clarity of his voice and christine’s like it really suits the phantom

i just love how husky it is and the low tones like ik he’s not a professional singer and he Barely uses like. feeling and emotion. but his singing voice is my favorite among all the phantoms i’ve heard
